channel.title: Modern Picture of the Alien
channel.description:
Who came up with the picture of aliens we have today..?
Just because they are from space doesn't mean they have 4 fingers (thumb included), no hair, and huge eyes.
Heres a ref pic: http://defensetech.org/2008/07/25/nasa-naut-claims-alien-coverup/

Of all the stars in this Universe(s?) there are most likely other life somewhere. Who’s to say it is intelligent? There probably are ET who either are not intelligent, intelligent and not aware of our existence, intelligent and aware but don’t care, or intelligent and they actually have visited our planet. I don’t know whether to believe we have been visited or not, but I for one believe there are other life forms somewhere in this Universe(s?). Scientists say other life forms would need some things we do, but some may actually don’t need oxygen, or water.
